{When SOUTH opens with a Weak 2\H bid, NORTH knows she will 
force to game but is thinking about slam. 

But first she needs to know if SOUTH has anything extra. She bids 2NT to get more information.

SOUTH returns to \Hs to show bare minimum so NORTH settles for game.}

